{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_10", "eventName": "破碎日冕", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "10-5", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "城市的呼吸", "storyInfo": "幾番試探之下，神秘人物自報家門，原來他們是倫蒂尼姆市民自救軍。地下通道內，自救軍隊長費斯特向阿米婭等人介紹了倫蒂尼姆的形勢。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_ventilatingduct_climb", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$blooddrop"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "27_i20", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "管道。幽深的，一眼望不到頭的管道。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些管道連通了整座城市。它們是倫蒂尼姆的血管，源源不斷地將能量輸送至倫蒂尼姆的心臟，也就是我們所在的位置。"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要畏懼你眼前的黑暗。太陽在每個傍晚落下，而陰影會在城市的脈管中永生。"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當光明被奪走，你需要更信任你的雙耳、你的鼻腔、你的其餘感官。"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請仔細聆聽吧。機械轟鳴即是血液奔湧，齒輪轉動應和呼吸節律。"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$blooddrop"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，倫蒂尼姆是活著的。無論我們在不在那高高的座椅上，它都有著自己的生命力。"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果有一天，你又一次來到這裡......無論那時在背後追逐著你的是什麼，你都無需感到害怕。"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為你奔跑在倫蒂尼姆的身體裡。"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，你回家了。"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "stopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g7_subway", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$escape_intro", "key": "$escape_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#4$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，各位，我們可以先在這裡停一停。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_411_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，這是什麼怪地方？", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#6$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_411_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們從上面一路爬下來，好像鑽進了一個什麼管道......", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#6$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_411_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "可露希爾", "content": "路是寬敞了不少，可是好黑呀......"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_411_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "可露希爾", "content": "嗚哇！你不會是想把我們拐到什麼廢棄工地，然後殺人滅口吧！"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哈？咳咳，也許，你說得沒錯。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#11$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，你小子到底什麼來頭？別以為我們真的會聽你擺佈！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#7$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......保險起見，這個問題我需要先問問你們。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#8$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們到底是什麼人？為什麼想要混進倫蒂尼姆？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......在我們做出任何回答之前，請你放開我們的人。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "是啊，我還在你手裡呢。;......;快把我放了。", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line61", "option2": "line61", "option3": "line61"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這兜帽朋友是你們的指揮官？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，我看到是誰在戰鬥中發號施令了。但是卡特斯小姐，你才是那個帶隊的人，對吧？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別露出這麼驚訝的眼神。你們是藏了幾手，可我們是......是本地人，這套玩得比你們熟得多。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 本地人......你們是倫蒂尼姆的居民？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 剛才那場混戰，你們也有參與？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別猜。卡特斯小姐，我們彼此還不夠信任。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是和深池還有薩卡茲動了下武，並不能說明什麼。他們之間也常常打架，這並不意味著我們應當和他們某一方交朋友。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......倫蒂尼姆的血管。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#4$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......你說什麼？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們已經來到倫蒂尼姆城內了。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼知道？！", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這些通道。它們內外連通，能讓我們繞開薩卡茲的守衛，直接從牆外抵達城內。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們走了多久？二十分鐘？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想，我們正處在倫蒂尼姆薩迪恩區的某一項關鍵設施的地下。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃......", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這設施離高牆不算遠。而且，它是一個樞紐，從這裡出發，能去很多地方......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......鐵軌。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再往前一到兩公里，我們頭頂就是車站。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你對倫蒂尼姆很熟悉。你也在這裡生活過？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"TIME": 0.51}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本地人。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難怪。我早就想說了，你的錘子讓我特別有親切感，菲林女士......呃，你是菲林吧？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你們是什麼，我就是什麼。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，要是你們真是薩卡茲派來的間諜，我是不是該後悔了？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#3$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不要傷害博士——！", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "他傷害不了我。;後悔也晚了。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line121", "option2": "line121"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......呃？！你......你什麼時候把無人機控制住了？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "竟、竟然徒手捏在手裡！你不怕我手裡有遙控器，直接引爆無人機上的炸彈？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "你沒有遙控器。;這無人機是個只會飛的半成品。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line129", "option2": "line129"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇，這下糟了。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#3$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你什麼時候發現的？在我和你們說話的時候，還是在帶你們進地下通道的時候？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是說更早......等等，你真的......在我抓住你的時候，就已經知道這無人機沒有威脅了？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你還任由我拉著你走來走去？！", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我要評估下你的意圖。;你以為我的同伴沒看出來嗎？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line141", "option2": "line141"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......假如你真表現出了傷害博士的意圖，在你的手碰到遙控器之前，我的錘子會先到你跟前。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說你呀，你要是抓一個傻一點的，比如我旁邊這個只會打拳的，搞不好還真能讓她上當哦？", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說什麼？你真以為他能靠近我？", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_411_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......這麼說，我偷偷準備好的無線電干擾器派不上用場了？", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#7$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ——“本地人”先生。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我想，這場互相試探的鬧劇是時候結束了。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#13$1"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 敵人的炮火雖然沒法追到這裡，可我們面臨的共同威脅並未遠去。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#13$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 請問我們是否已經展現了足夠的誠意？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#13$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 從剛見面開始，我們有無數機會對你動手。即便我們真的是薩卡茲的間諜，眼下也已經摸清楚了大致的方向，沒有必要再與你多費口舌。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#13$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 博士之所以能忍耐著扮演人質的角色，我們之所以願意隨你走入這地下通道，都是因為我們願意相信你沒有惡意。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 相應地，你是不是也可以再多信任我們一些，告訴我們你的真實意圖？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，這些話聽起來很有說服力。畢竟，眼下我也算你們的人質了。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "洛洛，出來吧。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drone"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_411_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無、無無無人機......？這麼多？！這陣勢是把我們都瞄準了？我們豈不是......豈不是隨時都可能被射成馬蜂窩？", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#5$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "洛洛，別費勁指著他們了。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#3$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管他們有沒有發現你和無人機，以他們的實力，真打起來的話，我可是壓根沒有逃命的機會啊。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#3$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "心裡有數的話，下回就別拉上我玩這無聊的遊戲了。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，你說得對。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#8$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，兜帽朋友，你能把洛克十七也還給我嗎？對，就你手裡那個無人機......我剛做了一半，你真捏壞了它，洛洛會生氣的。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼......現在，我們該重新認識一下了。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我叫費斯特，這位是洛洛，我的搭檔。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#5$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們隸屬於......倫蒂尼姆市民自救軍。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g4_giantwall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你覺得，在倫蒂尼姆這座城市裡，有多少我們看不見的角落？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......無法計數。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾百上千的老工廠，四成已經廢棄，六成還在使用。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還在使用的那些多半是建在更老的工廠舊址上，每一處廠房都像一個裝滿了數百年工業垃圾的迷宮。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一座又一座廠房中間，填塞著更多貧民窟。就連城防軍高層都說不出來，這些民用工業區和老物流區到底有多少人口。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有時候，我會覺得這裡和我們的卡茲戴爾並沒有多少區別。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們只是多造了一層光鮮的外殼，好把那些腐臭的部分埋得更深一些，以免熏到了那些體面的大人物。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#3$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_393_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......想在三天之內從卡茲戴爾貧民窟裡抓出一群鬧事的人，難度無異於單槍匹馬打劫一支有教宗騎士坐鎮的拉特蘭使節團。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#5$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那還是建立在我們都出生在卡茲戴爾的基礎上。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倫蒂尼姆......誰敢說自己熟悉倫蒂尼姆？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#7$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們擊潰議會的衛隊，拿下七成倫蒂尼姆城防軍的控制權，花了多久？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不到一周。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們吊死了幾個領頭反對的貴族，數十次打退他們花錢雇來的烏合之眾，直到把他們管得服服貼貼，又花了多久？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個半月。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我們在薩迪恩區，和那群自詡反抗軍的人在大街小巷裡來回拉鋸，已經過去好幾個月。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "半年時間，我們幾乎控制住了倫蒂尼姆的其他全部區塊。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唯獨這裡。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一塊半廢棄的民用工業用地，從南到北，環繞倫蒂尼姆中心的山體，連通著無人問津的老物流區......", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“倫蒂尼姆的歷史由此發源。”", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每一本史書上都會這麼寫。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道諸王之中，有一位或者幾位對我至今的戰果很不滿意。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_393_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說過。他們一直想徹底封鎖這塊城區。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#5$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們太容易被激怒。一旦指揮權落到他們手裡，他們就會用倫蒂尼姆人的屍體在薩迪恩區與其他區塊之間築起高牆。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少攝政王支援你。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，赫德雷，是我要盡全力支持將軍。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "王庭總是不理解將軍的苦心......他們並不理解眼前的平衡是多麼脆弱。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道我為何堅持暫時只啟動城防副炮嗎？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倘若我現在就啟動主炮......城外的大公爵會不會一齊向城內邁步？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倘若我們真的大肆屠殺倫蒂尼姆平民，城內的貴族與投向我們的城防軍，會不會再起異心，與我們鱗死網破？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倘若我們徹底放棄這塊工業區，沒了每天用列車送往碎片大廈的材料，將軍的計畫又要被迫延遲多久？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諸王的驕傲不容許他們低下古老的頭顱，來多看一眼這異邦的都城。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我看來，想徹底掌控倫蒂尼姆，最難打的仗就在眼前。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g7_subway", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲會叫我們反抗軍，我們對這個稱謂也沒什麼意見。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果只有站出來反抗他們才能救我們自己的話，那最普通的倫蒂尼姆人都會拿起武器。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你知道倫蒂尼姆其他區塊的情況如何嗎？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不會比這裡更好。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#4$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有人，要嘛為薩卡茲工作，要嘛丟掉性命。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#3$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陸陸續續有消息從北邊傳過來，我只聽說那裡的薩卡茲軍隊手段比這裡的還狠。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，留下來的貝爾德她們豈不是......", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別著急。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#8$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我怎麼能不急！五年，我們走了五年，我都不知道她們是不是已經......", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#7$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我們會找到她們的。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很快，我們會把她們一個個找回來。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#6$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，維娜，我相信你。不管她們在哪裡，不管她們是生是......", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉！我不在你面前說喪氣話！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女士們，只要你們的朋友還活著，我們總有辦法聯繫上她們。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們......不光在薩迪恩區活動？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#8$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們可以在倫蒂尼姆的任何地方，甚至城外。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們每抓走我們中的一個，就會有十個人站出來加入我們。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "洛洛是土生土長的薩迪恩區人，她是我們的元老成員之一，她最清楚，我們的隊伍是怎樣一點點壯大的。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......連你都當上小隊長了，我看人員增長速度是有點快。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，是誰帶你打了十一場勝仗啊，副隊長？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#9$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是到處把人救到地下，這也算勝仗嗎？", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能在薩卡茲眼皮子底下搶回一條命，保留一些暗地裡活動的機會......不就是勝利？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#7$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們都瞧見了，薩卡茲還沒有徹底掌控薩迪恩區。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的地形與人流都足夠亂，如果薩卡茲想掌握地上地下的每一塊能讓人呼吸的空間，他們得用自己的雙腳丈量個好幾年。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且......這裡也是最後一支倫蒂尼姆城防軍的隊伍與薩卡茲作戰的地方。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 看樣子他們也輸了。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，真打輸了也就輸了。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#4$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那場戰鬥結束得很快......有點太快了。在所有人反應過來之前，薩卡茲就已經站在了城牆上。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#4$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 全都是因為那幫叛徒！他們蛀空了我們的精銳部隊。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#7$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女士，你曾經是軍隊的人？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#5$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#3$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不，我不算是。我只是......呃，和她們一樣的本地人。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，本地人。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們都知道軍隊內部確實有叛徒，數量還不少。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "叛徒們和部分貴族率領著大部分城防軍一起投向了薩卡茲。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除了薩迪恩區，在大街小巷上巡邏的依然可能是“倫蒂尼姆城防軍”。只是他們的長官，已經成了薩卡茲宴會上的常客。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 那在附近作戰的最後一支隊伍......", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們堅持到了最後，每一個士兵都付出了慘痛的代價。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不清楚他們之中有多少還活著......但是我想，經歷了那樣無望的戰鬥之後，每看一眼如今倫蒂尼姆的高牆，他們都會很痛苦吧。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g9_lightinduarea_street_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不必這麼警惕。抬起頭，把手從弩上鬆開，姿勢稍微放鬆一些。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 咳，咳咳。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 附近的居民習慣了各式各樣的人從這裡經過。他們並不會幫我們，但只要不是性命受到威脅，他們也絕不會聽命於深池和薩卡茲。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 在這些敵人眼皮底下生活......恐怕很不容易。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你知道他們以前是怎麼看待我們的嗎？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 呃，我沒有想過。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我以前也不會去想。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 中尉......", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 對了，在外面不要叫我中尉。還是叫號角吧，這地方屬於不同部隊的“中尉”數量過多了。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#6$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 是，號角。我們要去哪裡？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我們先去和其他同伴會合。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 薩卡茲的巡邏隊會在五分鐘後路過這一帶。我們分成兩隊，先後沿著前面的鐵軌往東走。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 三百五十米之後，你們會看到一截往上走的鐵皮樓梯。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 要是聽到五下金屬敲擊聲，你們就可以跟上來。三下，原地等待。兩下，立刻解散。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 也許你會覺得那一片廢棄廠區很眼熟......別太驚訝，那裡也是深池的駐地。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 這......豈不是會很危險？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 有深池在，至少薩卡茲很少來。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 想不想試試看捉迷藏？歡迎加入這場遊戲。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#6$1"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g7_subway", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$farce_intro", "key": "$farce_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說，你們真的只是一家普通企業？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "和你是一名機械工程師一樣貨真價實。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line416"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 417, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈......言簡意賅。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#9$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然薩卡茲都能當倫蒂尼姆的頭兒，我又有什麼理由懷疑你們的說辭呢？醫療企業的安保人員，對吧？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#9$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看看......一支十七個人的小隊，攜帶著軍用級的裝備，加上不錯的戰術配合，甚至還有著挺像那麼回事的無人機。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#9$1"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_411_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......“像那麼回事”？", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#11$1"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_411_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼叫“像那麼回事”？這評價簡直太不像話了！", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#4$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸欸，別生氣呀。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#3$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛在上面沒看清楚，要不你什麼時候再給我多看兩眼？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#9$1"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_411_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......都被薩卡茲炸毀了啊！這麼一想簡直更心疼了！", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#11$1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不試著修一修嗎？你一定留了幾架殘骸吧，要不然我幫你看看，我有全套工具。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#7$1"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 可露希爾，我剛剛的確搶下來兩架......", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 439, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "無人機是羅德島的技術。; 得先合作，再技術交流。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line444", "option2": "line447"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line450"}, {"id": 445, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來我得拿好東西來換？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#7$1"}, {"id": 447, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line450"}, {"id": 448, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇，這麼警惕？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#11$1"}, {"id": 450, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 451, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士......你到底是什麼領域的博士啊？算了算了，有機會再說吧，反正我不著急。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#11$1"}, {"id": 453, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比起這個，你們到底是怎麼來到倫蒂尼姆的？我跟你們說了不少城內的情況了，看在雙向合作的份上，說說外面的情況吧？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#5$1"}, {"id": 455, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 456, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......這條路有點長。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}, {"id": 457, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 458, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，你們已經和深池交過手了。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 459, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#18$1"}}, {"id": 460, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你們在城外也有眼線？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#18$1"}, {"id": 461, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 462, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡特斯小姐，我們說好了，情報需要交換。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 463, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 464, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......好。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 465, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1"}}, {"id": 466, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 按時間遠近倒過來說的話，在倫蒂尼姆外面的附屬地塊，我們與深池之間確實發生了一場戰鬥......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1"}, {"id": 467, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 468, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 469, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 470, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 471, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 472, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 473, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}